data.description: Come see this move in ready home.  There is plenty of space to breathe in this large 4 bedroom, 2 bath rancher/ rambler home located conveniently in Malaga just a hop skip and jump to route 55,  a major roadway access that points you to  Philadelphia or down to the Shore within about 40 minutes. You'll enter into a large  Kitchen with tons of natural light and windows along with high hat LED lights and under the cabinet to set a beautiful ambiance! The Kitchen has been completely renovated and includes newer stainless appliances. The Kitchen steps down to the entrance of an the over-sized newer vinyl  fenced in yard that offers many options to make it your own and enjoy years of outdoor activities and family gatherings under the pergola.Next to the pergola, you will find a generously 3 bay garage which one of the bays have been transitioned into a detached accessory dwelling with a heat, cable, hook-ups for stove and sink.  There is a main bedroom includes a private bathroom with stand up shower that has been freshly painted with new trim. There are three more generously sized bedrooms with plenty of storage space for the whole family. As you make your way downstairs you will see a full footprint unfinished basement that would be perfect as extra storage or if your imagination runs wild there are many possibilities to have the finished basement of your dreams. In addition the the spacious living quarters, there is a ton of storage in a full length walkable attic with fans and lighting. While you are out looking for homes make sure to add this one to the list and come check it out!!
